1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 26=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(What? A Lifetime Contract)

4
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:55,040
What are you two up to this time?

5
00:00:55,680 --> 00:00:56,560
Fine then.

6
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:58,440
Let's

7
00:00:59,120 --> 00:01:00,300
- settle this.
- Settle this.

8
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,720
The winner takes all.

9
00:01:49,380 --> 00:01:50,200
I accept my defeat.

10
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:52,640
Yuanhe.

11
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:55,880
Do it.

12
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:13,480
Take this traitorous son away.

13
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:15,880
Exile him to the southern frontier.

14
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,680
He is never to return.

15
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,720
If you dare come back,

16
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,680
I will have you executed.

17
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:51,200
As Crown Prince,
you use one royal title.

18
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:55,400
As Emperor, you use another.

19
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,800
What a load of nonsense.

20
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,320
In the end,

21
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:14,520
you're still nothing but a lonely ruler.

22
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:23,960
Move.

23
00:03:28,980 --> 00:03:31,180
(Zhao Prince's Residence)

24
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:39,240
Your Highness.

25
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,760
This is all the silver

26
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:42,190
confiscated from
the Second Prince's Residence.

27
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:44,080
That's my bank's silver.

28
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:46,800
I can finally pay off my debts
and get my life back on track.

29
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,800
Does your name
happen to be written on it?

30
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:52,520
I...

31
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,750
This is stolen silver confiscated from
the Second Prince's Residence.

32
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,270
Every tael will be turned over
to the national treasury.

33
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:58,480
I knew you'd never change.

34
00:03:58,480 --> 00:03:59,440
You jerk.

35
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:01,920
That's my money!

36
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:02,760
You can't take it.

37
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,120
Unless...

38
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,880
Unless what?

39
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,720
Sign this contract.

40
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:14,880
Then every tael

41
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,280
will be returned to you.

42
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,600
Copycat.

43
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:21,160
Are you still holding a grudge

44
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,900
over making you leave
your thumbprint before?

45
00:04:23,980 --> 00:04:24,740
(Contract)

46
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:27,720
Li Qingqing, Tower Master
of Wangshi Tower, hereby guarantees

47
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:31,080
that she and all businesses
and shops under her name

48
00:04:31,100 --> 00:04:33,160
shall, from this day forward,
voluntarily submit to

49
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:35,280
the supervision
of Crown Prince Zheng Yuanhe.

50
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:40,720
Li Qingqing must first notify
Crown Prince Zheng Yuanhe

51
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:43,400
of all dealings with any third party.

52
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:46,000
Zheng Yuanhe shall have
the power of final veto.

53
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:50,160
(Contract)
The term of this contract shall be for life.

54
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:51,840
Seriously?

55
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:59,000
At least mine was a proper contract.

56
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,560
You need termination terms
and an expiration date.

57
00:05:01,570 --> 00:05:03,510
This is nothing
but a one sided lifetime contract.

58
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,600
For life?

59
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,440
What else?

60
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,200
Should I let you take all this silver

61
00:05:08,210 --> 00:05:10,500
and go back to being the lawless
Tower Master of Wangshi Tower?

62
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:12,520
Building catapults
and stockpiling gunpowder,

63
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:13,920
blowing up anyone you don't like,

64
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:16,400
only to end up arrested
as a rebel again?

65
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,600
Rest assured.

66
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:25,760
I have no intention
of taking your silver.

67
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:28,880
Sign this contract,

68
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,640
and not only can you use this silver
to repay your debts,

69
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:33,200
you'll also have me backing you,

70
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,700
making it easier
to expand your trade routes.

71
00:05:36,080 --> 00:05:39,000
(Signing this means
he'll have me under his thumb forever.)

72
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:42,080
(But if I don't sign,
I'll have to keep running.)

73
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:44,120
(Always afraid
of being branded a rebel.)

74
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:48,680
The brush.

75
00:05:56,260 --> 00:05:58,180
(Contract)

76
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,120
Chang Lin.

77
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:00,560
Yes.

78
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,480
Help Miss Li
take these back to Wangshi Tower.

79
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:02,880
Yes.

80
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:05,400
Now all this silver is mine.

81
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,860
(It doesn't matter
if you still don't understand love.)

82
00:06:13,100 --> 00:06:15,080
(I'll spend the rest of my life
waiting for you.)

83
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,720
My silver.

84
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:28,680
By the Mandate of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees:

85
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,280
Li,

86
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:31,280
Li Qingqing,

87
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,040
founder of Wangshi Tower,

88
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,080
has enriched Great Yong's treasury,

89
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,600
assisted the Crown Prince
in eliminating the rebels,

90
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:41,160
and by means of newspapers,
attracted scholars of humble origins

91
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,320
to strive for a better future,

92
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:45,080
bringing worthy men into service

93
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,900
and restoring integrity
to the imperial court.

94
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:49,190
In recognition of Qingqing's
loyal and virtuous heart,

95
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,320
I hereby pardon
Wangshi Tower of all its crimes.

96
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,560
So decreed.

97
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,920
Thank you, Your Majesty.

98
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,040
Rise.

99
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,200
Qingqing.

100
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,400
Although Wangshi Tower
has been pardoned,

101
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,760
but,

102
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:08,000
the newspapers have a profound influence

103
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,640
on public opinion in Great Yong.

104
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:12,920
They will inevitably
be subject to imperial oversight.

105
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,520
Naturally.

106
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:16,880
Newspapers are a double edged sword.

107
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,560
Without proper oversight,

108
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,160
they are bound to breed chaos.

109
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,840
Well said.

110
00:07:23,660 --> 00:07:25,560
As for Wangshi Tower
and the Wangshi Chronicle,

111
00:07:25,840 --> 00:07:26,720
from this day forward,

112
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,640
the Crown Prince and the Inspectorate

113
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,480
shall oversee them together.

114
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:35,760
I accept

115
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:36,940
Your Majesty's decree.

116
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,760
(Why can't I get rid of him?)

117
00:07:48,220 --> 00:07:49,700
(Pan Residence)

118
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,120
It was Pan Yang and Li Muyan

119
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,320
who betrayed His Highness.

120
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:54,280
Arrest them.

121
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:56,760
Two ungrateful traitors.
What a shameless pair.

122
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:59,700
Before they're taken to
the Inspectorate, let me beat them first.

123
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:04,000
Yang, what do we do now?

124
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,840
We've offended His Highness.

125
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,240
There's only one way out.

126
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,680
You mean

127
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,240
the Tower Master?

128
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:13,000
That's right.

129
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,120
The deed we just sold

130
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,800
can be our offering

131
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:20,160
to join Wangshi Tower.

132
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:21,280
Exactly.

133
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:23,200
Merchants put profit first.

134
00:08:23,210 --> 00:08:25,160
The Tower Master
is a businesswoman after all.

135
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,680
With these gold bars,

136
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,740
getting into Wangshi Tower
shouldn't be difficult.

137
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,280
Let's go.

138
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:39,440
Pan Yang of the Pan family

139
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:41,480
wishes to serve under the Tower Master.

140
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,920
I humbly request an audience.

141
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,480
Tower Master,

142
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:47,920
we only seek a place to settle down.

143
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:50,040
Please take us in.

144
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,600
It's only been a few days,

145
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:02,840
and you've already fallen this far.

146
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,440
Li Qingqing?

147
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:13,960
Why are you here?

148
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:18,000
Tower Master,

149
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,520
Li Qingqing

150
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,600
is immoral

151
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,440
and full of lies.

152
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,920
She must have slandered Yang and me.

153
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,840
Please see the truth, Tower Master.

154
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:28,440
Open your eyes and look carefully.

155
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:30,520
Miss Qingqing is the Tower Master
of Wangshi Tower.

156
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:36,800
She...

157
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:39,120
This...

158
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:39,800
She...

159
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:41,400
She's the Tower Master?

160
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:43,920
How...

161
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:45,480
How is that possible?

162
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,280
Didn't see that coming, did you?

163
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,400
Let's see

164
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:54,520
what the Dark Hall has

165
00:09:56,560 --> 00:09:58,480
for you two to try.

166
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,240
Li Qingqing,

167
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,240
I... It was all...

168
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:06,240
It was all her fault.

169
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:07,920
It was all that wretched Li Muyan.

170
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:10,120
She faked her pregnancy
and tricked me with a child.

171
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,000
That's why I had no choice
but to marry her.

172
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:11,680
Pan Yang!

173
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:12,920
You jerk!

174
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,040
Qingqing...

175
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,000
Tower Master,

176
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:17,080
it was him!

177
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:19,960
He only wanted my status
as the Li family's daughter.

178
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:20,840
What status?

179
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,480
He even said...

180
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,200
He even said...

181
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,000
You wasn't feminine enough.

182
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:27,790
He forced and deceived me
into marrying into the Pan family.

183
00:10:27,800 --> 00:10:29,440
I'm a victim too!

184
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:31,800
You

185
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,720
don't turn on each other.

186
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,200
You dared help the Second Prince

187
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:52,200
stage a coup.

188
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:54,440
Now no one can save you.

189
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,660
Take them to the Inspectorate first.

190
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,040
Once they're convicted,

191
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:03,520
exile them to the northern wastelands.

192
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:04,240
Yes.

193
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,040
Your Highness.

194
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,480
I... I confess.

195
00:11:08,680 --> 00:11:10,080
I only have one request.

196
00:11:10,760 --> 00:11:11,480
Your Highness.

197
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:12,240
Say it.

198
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,560
Even if I die,

199
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:16,360
I refuse to be exiled with Pan Yang.

200
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:18,560
Please grant my request.

201
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,640
As if I'd want to go with you!

202
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,040
Your Highness.

203
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:24,200
I have a request too.

204
00:11:24,210 --> 00:11:25,950
I want to be exiled
to the southern frontier.

205
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,470
The farther from this woman, the better.

206
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:27,920
You...

207
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:29,400
Pan Yang, you heartless brute!

208
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:31,480
- You venomous woman. Drop the act!
- And now you're blaming me? What kind of man are you?

209
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,240
You short-legged husband!

210
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:32,840
I'll kick you to death!

211
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,000
- Who are you calling short?
- Take them away.

212
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,000
What an eyesore.

213
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:36,990
- Your Highness!
- Take them away.

214
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:40,440
Spare us, Your Highness!

215
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:41,840
Tower Master!

216
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:43,480
Tower Master!

217
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:46,080
Please spare us!

218
00:11:52,560 --> 00:11:54,040
You've worked hard, Your Highness.

219
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:57,800
I'm sure you have
many matters to attend to.

220
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:59,160
I won't keep you any longer.

221
00:12:02,760 --> 00:12:04,240
Have you forgotten my duty?

222
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,240
What?

223
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:07,800
To oversee Wangshi Tower.

224
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,720
These are the troops I brought.

225
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,960
They're also here to protect you.

226
00:12:17,280 --> 00:12:18,640
What's all this?

227
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:22,160
Why are there quilts too?

228
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,480
You

229
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,920
think too much.

230
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:29,520
I need to keep an eye on you
at all times.

231
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:31,720
From now on,

232
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,800
this will be my permanent residence.

233
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:35,320
I...

234
00:12:35,680 --> 00:12:36,160
Wait.

235
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,800
I haven't agreed to this.

236
00:12:37,880 --> 00:12:38,240
No...

237
00:12:38,690 --> 00:12:40,080
I mean, you're the Crown Prince.

238
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,890
Are you really going to
be my lapdog for life?

239
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,200
Qingqing,

240
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:46,920
why are you calling yourself a dog?

241
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:47,400
I...

242
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:47,920
I

243
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:49,280
won't allow it.

244
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:53,080
Why are you carrying me inside?

245
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,520
To teach you how to love me.

246
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:58,160
I... I do seem to like you a little.

247
00:12:58,520 --> 00:12:59,960
But you have to take it slow.

248
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:00,520
I...

249
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:02,520
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

250
00:13:02,760 --> 00:13:03,320
Jiuzhu!

251
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,240
Jiuzhu!

252
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:05,400
Jiu

253
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:08,000
(Wangshi Tower)
Zhu!

254
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:10,660
(Wangshi Tower)

255
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,680
This is so annoying.

256
00:13:16,060 --> 00:13:17,420
(Wangshi Tower)

257
00:13:17,420 --> 00:13:23,620
(Jin Family
Eight Immortals Tea House)

258
00:13:27,740 --> 00:13:32,980
(To be continued)

259
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:42,430
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

260
00:13:43,190 --> 00:13:46,570
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

261
00:13:47,340 --> 00:13:49,080
♪Your smile♪

262
00:13:49,340 --> 00:13:51,630
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

263
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:55,310
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

264
00:13:55,770 --> 00:13:59,080
♪Yet I stand before you♪

265
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:03,650
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

266
00:14:04,070 --> 00:14:05,990
♪Though fate tries♪

267
00:14:05,990 --> 00:14:08,570
♪To make us pass each other by♪

268
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:12,210
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

269
00:14:12,470 --> 00:14:14,100
♪Though time slips by♪

270
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:15,860
♪As day turns into night♪

271
00:14:16,380 --> 00:14:20,400
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

272
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:23,200
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

273
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,990
♪Blessed by fate♪

274
00:14:24,990 --> 00:14:30,150
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

275
00:14:30,150 --> 00:14:32,590
♪Your smiling face♪

276
00:14:32,590 --> 00:14:35,430
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

277
00:14:35,430 --> 00:14:39,050
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

278
00:14:39,570 --> 00:14:43,030
♪And wander the world together♪

279
00:14:43,030 --> 00:14:44,370
♪Holding you close♪

280
00:14:44,370 --> 00:14:46,910
